author: Asha Prakash
title: Annie would have made a good businesswoman
text:
Balachandra Menon, who has introduced some of the best actresses to Mollywood, was recently asked who his finds would have been had they not been spotted by him.
"Karthika would have been a doctor. Parvathy would have been a homemaker. As for Annie, she knows who to conduct herself in society so she would have made a good business woman," commented the director-actor, who was the guest at Onnum Onnum Moonnu, hosted by Rimi Tomy.
